---
title: Seared Scallop and Creamy Bacon Linguine with Lemon and Baby Plum Tomato & Rocket Salad
description: Treat yourself this May Bank Holiday with this Seared Scallop and Creamy Bacon Linguine. This dish takes inspiration from classic restaurant dishes with a gourmet protein to bring a fine dining experience straight into your home!

Say hello to a fresh ingredient - scallops! Noted for their beautiful fan-like shells and delicate flavour, scallops are no doubt a real 'catch' for dinner.
